        "Abstract": "This paper presents RuBia, a novel dataset for bias detection in Russian language models. The dataset consists of 1989 sentence pairs, each pair consisting of a pro-trope sentence and an anti-trope sentence. The dataset is divided into four domains: gender, nationality, socio-economic status, and diverse. The paper also evaluates the bias of nine widely used language models using the RuBia dataset."
